These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, turtle
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, ebony, white
1. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Pet     | chinchilla | dog    | turtle   |
| Color   | brown  | white | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, fish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, satire, scientific
1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Pet      | lizard   | fish  | frog |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | family | scientific    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, russian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, adventure, epic
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
2. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
3. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
4. the russian is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | russian | chinese |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure    | epic     | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, plum, tomato
3 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, domino
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
2. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
4. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Food    | tomato | corn     | plum   |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | monopoly | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, trike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | scientific | thriller   |
| Transport     | scooter | trike    | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, rock-climbing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, water
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | gardening | dancing | rock-climbing |
| Beverage   | milk   | juice   | water        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, tulip
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
3. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| Flower     | rose | tulip    | orchid |
| Sport   | badminton      | volleyball | skiing             |

