.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, drawing, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, musical, adventure
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
4. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | reading | drawing  | baking    |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure   | action | musical |

