.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, photography
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, reggae, salsa
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
3. the fan of house is between the fan of salsa and the fan of reggae##2
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby           | puzzles | chess | photography |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | house      | salsa    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-11::.
