.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, metal, r&b
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5
3. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Music-Genre        | disco | metal | r&b |
| Transport   | subway  | bus         | train   |

