.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | sprite   | cola   |
| Sport   | badminton | basketball | biathlon |

