2. the french is on the left or right of the british##3
3. the russian is on the right of the french##1
4. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Nationality   | british | french       | russian |
| Food         | spinach | tomato | eggplant |

