1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Transport   | motorbike | tram | jet-ski |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | fish    | dog    |

