.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-20::.
City: edinburgh, marseilles, colone
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, tram, van
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |  3   |
| City   | marseilles | edinburgh | colone  |
| Transport     | scooter | van   | tram |

 